item.description:
@system wrote:

Ayush Arya:

Help! People can’t connect to my server also status checkers say that my server is offline.It also won’t let me log in.I have PI DSPK InsidiaX Source and client.I’ve portforwarded firewalled.Changed Ip in both server and client.In server i changed in server.java.In client I did changed in client.java and gui.java help me plz

  1. Read through the replys at PI DSPK InsidiaX Source and client 65% of the posts there are because of this, your not the only one having this issue. It is possible out of the 27 pages of posts someone has already resolved this problem.

  2. Can you compile, or does it give you errors?

  3. Have you ran it locally before you tried port forwarding it to your friends.

  4. try running a different source+ client if this works, then we know that its a problem with the InsidiaX, if not then theirs a problem with your port-forwarding.
